我会做Maher所要求的 我们去跟其他们交代一下
I'll do what Maher wants.Let's brief the others.

167
00:13:05,253 --> 00:13:08,165
Sam Richards现在已经干过moores银行四个分部了
Sam Richards has now hit four branches of Moores Bank.

168
00:13:08,253 --> 00:13:10,926
我们有密报他打算抢伦敦的分公司
We got a tip-off he's due to hit the London branch.

169
00:13:11,013 --> 00:13:12,128
我不明白
I don't get it.

170
00:13:12,213 --> 00:13:15,888
- 什么时候开始我们开始抢银行了? - 不是我们.是Richards
- Since when do we rob banks? - We don't.Richards is going to.

171
00:13:17,093 --> 00:13:18,367
那,内容是?
So what's the con?

172
00:13:18,453 --> 00:13:21,604
不管怎样这都会发生 我们只是事后分杯羹
It's going to happen anyway.We just take a slice after the fact.

173
00:13:21,693 --> 00:13:24,526
哦,怎么我听起来还是像抢银行
Well,that still sounds like robbing banks to me.

174
00:13:24,613 --> 00:13:27,446
什么时候开始,我们问去哪里拿钱了??
Since when did we ask where a mark got his money?

175
00:13:27,533 --> 00:13:30,206
如果他已经接受了这件事情 那会给他一个公平的游戏
If it's going down anyway,then it makes him fair game.

176
00:13:30,293 --> 00:13:34,252
哦,我们成了附属品了,无论是之前,过程中,还是之后
Yeah,and it makes us accessories before,during,and after the fact.

177
00:13:34,333 --> 00:13:38,087
厨房已经空了,伙计们,我们 需要点成绩,而且要快
The cupboard is bare.Guys,we need a score and we need it fast.

178
00:13:43,413 --> 00:13:44,766
我同意Michael的意见
I'm with Michael.

179
00:13:45,613 --> 00:13:47,683
好吧,那我们知道他多少?
Okay,so what do we know about him?

180
00:13:47,773 --> 00:13:50,571
不多,除了他不喜欢银行
Not much,except that he seems to dislike banks.

181
00:13:50,653 --> 00:13:52,166
谁喜欢呢?
Who doesn't?

182
00:13:52,293 --> 00:13:53,612
那,怎么做?
So what's the in?

183
00:13:53,853 --> 00:13:55,684
他需要一个警报专家
He needs an alarms expert.

184
00:13:55,773 --> 00:13:57,331
我们让Ash做诱饵
We use Ash as the bait.

185
00:13:57,413 --> 00:13:59,085
你对警报系统了解吗?
What do you know about alarms?

186
00:13:59,173 --> 00:14:01,687
- 我无所不知 - 你无所不知?
- I know about everything. - You know about everything?

187
00:14:01,773 --> 00:14:04,003
好吧,既然如此
Okay,if you know about everything...

188
00:14:04,093 --> 00:14:07,449
卢森堡首都是哪里?
what's the capital of Luxembourg?

189
00:14:07,733 --> 00:14:09,052
卢森堡城
Luxembourg City.

190
00:14:09,413 --> 00:14:11,881
- 好,你太棒了 - 谢谢夸奖
- You're good,you're very good. - Thank you very much.

191
00:14:11,973 --> 00:14:13,770
你别无聊了,Danny
You're not helping,Danny.

192
00:14:15,213 --> 00:14:19,206
不要开始把矛头对准我,小妞 就因为你已经看过我裸体
Don't start having a go at me,girl,just because you've seen me naked.

193
00:14:20,933 --> 00:14:22,207
别问了
Don't ask.

194
00:14:24,093 --> 00:14:25,492
好了,这就是我们要干的
Okay,this is what we do.

195
00:14:26,213 --> 00:14:29,046
<i>Richards现在皇家旅馆</i>
<i>Richards is staying at the Royal Lodge Hotel.</i>

196
00:14:29,893 --> 00:14:32,088
<i>Albert从那儿钓他上钩</i>
<i>Albert will hook him in from there.</i>

197
00:14:32,533 --> 00:14:34,046
<i>一旦他联系上</i>
<i>Once he's made contact...</i>

198
00:14:34,133 --> 00:14:36,522
<i>他把我作为当地的毒贩子介绍给他</i>
<i>he introduces him to me as a local fixer...</i>

199
00:14:36,613 --> 00:14:38,171
<i>我再把他介绍给Ash</i>
<i>and I pass him on to Ash.</i>

200
00:14:38,253 --> 00:14:39,845
Danny和我做什么?
What about Danny and me?

201
00:14:39,933 --> 00:14:42,322
你们两个机动,补空档
We keep you two floating,plug any gaps.

202
00:14:44,733 --> 00:14:46,769
好了,来吧,干起来
Okay,come on,let's do it.

203
00:14:54,813 --> 00:14:55,962
裸体?
Naked?

204
00:14:56,333 --> 00:14:58,244
- 剥猪猡 - 是的
- Strip poker. - Right.

205
00:14:59,533 --> 00:15:01,922
- 你吃醋了 - 没有
- You were jealous. - No,I wasn't.

206
00:15:02,013 --> 00:15:03,446
- 才怪 - 真没有
- Yes,you were. - No.

207
00:15:03,533 --> 00:15:06,809
我只是担心你让他吃亏
I was just concerned you may have been taking advantage of him.

208
00:15:06,893 --> 00:15:08,292
当然
Of course you are.

209
00:15:09,453 --> 00:15:10,772
你能帮我个忙吗?
Can you do something for me?

210
00:15:10,853 --> 00:15:13,413
当然,如果你想的话,我现在就去拿牌
Yeah,I'll go and get the cards now if you like.

211
00:15:14,133 --> 00:15:16,522
不,我要你
No,I need you to...

212
00:15:16,613 --> 00:15:18,490
让Danny分神一会儿
keep Danny out of the way for a while.

213
00:15:18,573 --> 00:15:20,564
这很重要 我过后再跟你解释
It's important.I'll explain why later.

214
00:15:20,653 --> 00:15:21,927
他有麻烦了?
Is he in trouble?

215
00:15:22,013 --> 00:15:24,049
只要让他保持忙碌就行了
Just keep him occupied.

216
00:15:24,133 --> 00:15:26,089
- 好的 - 谢了
- Okay. - Thanks.

217
00:15:28,173 --> 00:15:29,401
我不敢相信
I don't believe this.

218
00:15:29,493 --> 00:15:32,053
英国银行税率多少?3.5%?
What is the Bank of England interest rate?3.5%?

219
00:15:32,133 --> 00:15:34,124
他们已经对我的信用卡收了我10倍
They've charged me 10 times this...

220
00:15:34,213 --> 00:15:37,091
这卡我一开始就不想要
for a credit card I didn't want in the first place.

221
00:15:48,173 --> 00:15:49,447
这什么?
What's all this?

222
00:15:51,173 --> 00:15:52,242
警报装置
Alarms.

223
00:15:52,333 --> 00:15:55,131
- 我以为你了解 - 我是了解,只是有点生锈了（不记得了）
- I thought you knew about alarms. - I do.I'm just a bit rusty.

224
00:15:55,213 --> 00:15:57,169
- 我们可是有时间限制的 - 我知道
- We're on a clock here. - I know.

225
00:15:59,573 --> 00:16:01,484
机动?这算什么?
Floating?What's that all about?

226
00:16:01,573 --> 00:16:03,131
你打算抱怨一整天?
Are you going to bitch all day?

227
00:16:03,213 --> 00:16:05,363
Albert,不错,他来做诱饵
Albert,okay,he's the roper.

228
00:16:05,453 --> 00:16:07,967
Ash来装配 Mickey,是局内人
Ash does the fixing.Mickey,inside man.

229
00:16:08,053 --> 00:16:12,285
我呢?机动人员 对我来说,听起来一无是处
Me?I'm a floater.To me that sounds like a turd.

230
00:16:12,573 --> 00:16:15,610
我们要成为核心人员,是不是,Danny?
And we do like to be center stage,don't we,Danny?

231
00:16:15,693 --> 00:16:19,129
我有才能 与全世界分享是我的责任
I have a talent.It's my duty to share it with the world.

232
00:16:19,213 --> 00:16:22,171
- 你想得真周到 - 嘿,我喜欢这份职业
- That's very thoughtful of you. - Hey,I love it.

233
00:16:22,413 --> 00:16:24,131
所以,那又怎么样?
So what's wrong with that?

234
00:16:24,453 --> 00:16:26,125
你告诉我你不喜欢吗?
You're telling me you don't?

235
00:16:26,213 --> 00:16:28,522
- 这是达成一个目的的一条途径 - 什么目的?
- It's a means to an end. - What end?

236
00:16:30,493 --> 00:16:34,566
有一天,攒够钱在加勒比海买个小地方 就这样
Saving enough money to buy a small place in the Caribbean one day.That's it.

237
00:16:34,653 --> 00:16:36,723
你是说这只是一份职业?
So you're saying it's just a job to you?

238
00:16:36,813 --> 00:16:38,087
我不是这个意思
I didn't say that.

239
00:16:38,173 --> 00:16:39,731
那你喜欢它吗?
So you love it really?

240
00:16:40,133 --> 00:16:41,771
这重要吗?
Is there any point to this?

241
00:16:41,853 --> 00:16:44,890
是的,你知道,这纵容了我
Yes.You know,indulge me.

242
00:16:45,253 --> 00:16:48,848
让我来告诉你 你干吗不告诉我关于你的事情?
I tell you what.Why don't you tell me about you?

243
00:17:02,373 --> 00:17:03,692
哈罗,又见面了
Hello,again.

244
00:17:04,453 --> 00:17:06,444
早餐的时候我们已经见过了
We met briefly at breakfast.

245
00:17:07,773 --> 00:17:09,729
是的,我记得,不好意思
Yeah,I remember.Sorry.

246
00:17:10,133 --> 00:17:12,169
- George Cooper - Sam Richards
- George Cooper. - Sam Richards.

247
00:17:12,733 --> 00:17:15,964
- 让我请你喝一杯吧 - 苏格兰威士忌,谢谢
- Can I get you a drink? - Scotch.Thanks.

248
00:17:18,213 --> 00:17:21,091
你早上看上去不太高兴
You look like a man who's had a tough morning.

249
00:17:21,813 --> 00:17:24,964
我在等个人,但他临时爽约了
I was expecting someone,but they've gone AWOL.

250
00:17:25,413 --> 00:17:28,689
- 有没有什么我能做的? - 哦不,恐怕不行
- Is there anything I can help you with? - No,I doubt it.

251
00:17:28,773 --> 00:17:31,970
请记住:不存在任何问题
Just remember:There are no such things as problems...

252
00:17:32,053 --> 00:17:34,521
只存在解决问题的机会
simply opportunities for solutions.

253
00:17:35,333 --> 00:17:37,403
谢谢,我会试着记住它
Thanks.I'll try and remember it.

254
00:17:39,413 --> 00:17:40,892
- 干杯 - 干杯
- Cheers. - Cheers.

255
00:17:42,773 --> 00:17:45,606
好了,伙计.我喜欢所有的老一辈骗术家
Okay,mate.I love all the old cons.

256
00:17:46,453 --> 00:17:48,523
你知道,他们在书中所写的那些
You know,stuff they wrote about in books...

257
00:17:48,613 --> 00:17:50,285
二三十年代时候的东西
in the '20s and '30s.

258
00:17:50,853 --> 00:17:53,811
例如Charles Ponzi,"黄色小子" Weil
People like Charles Ponzi,"Yellow Kid" Weil.

259
00:17:53,933 --> 00:17:56,493
- Danny,你真是个罗曼蒂克老手 - 我说吧...
- Danny,you're an old romantic. - See...

260
00:17:56,573 --> 00:17:58,484
我知道你对此不屑一顾
I knew you'd take the piss.

261
00:17:58,933 --> 00:18:01,766
不,我没有.我发誓
No,I'm not.I promise.

262
00:18:03,733 --> 00:18:07,169
我不知道,我只是总想试试身手
I don't know.I just always wanted to try one.

263
00:18:07,493 --> 00:18:09,768
- 看看是什么样的感觉 - 是的,我理解
- See what it'd feel like. - Well,then.

264
00:18:10,013 --> 00:18:11,332
你应该知道
You shall.

265
00:18:15,813 --> 00:18:17,804
拿我来说吧,我干保险业
Take my game.Insurance.

266
00:18:18,133 --> 00:18:19,486
去年我们声称
We had a claim last year...

267
00:18:19,573 --> 00:18:21,803
他妈的肯定有室内工作
that I was damn certain was an inside job.

268
00:18:21,893 --> 00:18:25,169
一个富丽堂皇的屋子里发生了盗窃 天衣无缝的保安系统
There was a burglary at a stately home.State-of-the-art security.

269
00:18:25,253 --> 00:18:27,164
他们来去
They were in and gone...

270
00:18:27,253 --> 00:18:30,450
抢走了珠宝,没有留下一点指纹
with the family jewels without so much as a footprint.

271
00:18:30,693 --> 00:18:33,253
问题是,我们不仅需要一个警报专家
Trouble was,not only did we need an alarms man...

272
00:18:33,333 --> 00:18:35,563
而且要是一个老手,告诉我们这个怎么做到的
but a crooked one to tell us how it was fixed.

273
00:18:35,653 --> 00:18:37,166
你找到了吗?
Did you find one?

274
00:18:38,453 --> 00:18:41,092
是的,幸运的是,我知道这么个人
Well,fortunately,I had a contact for that.

275
00:18:41,213 --> 00:18:44,967
极其缺乏职业道德,但非常出色
Terribly unethical,but needs must and all that.

276
00:18:49,333 --> 00:18:51,483
- 我再给你倒一杯? - 好的
- Can I get you another? - Yeah.

277
00:18:58,373 --> 00:19:00,887
是的,Albert?带他过来
Yeah,Albert?Bring him in.

278
00:19:03,133 --> 00:19:05,044
不,我不是故意的,别急
No,I meant to do that,don't worry.

279
00:19:05,933 --> 00:19:07,412
你听得见吗?
Can you hear me?

280
00:19:07,493 --> 00:19:08,812
我马上让它安静下来
I'll quiet it down for you.

281
00:19:16,773 --> 00:19:17,888
什么?
What?

282
00:19:45,273 --> 00:19:48,888
我和我的银行经理有个重要的会议 你能帮我照看一下狗吗?

283
00:20:24,873 --> 00:20:28,888
那是条很贵重的狗.是你的吗?我愿出高价来买它

284
00:21:18,273 --> 00:21:22,188
银行经理在贷款部给我打电话 我破产了!

285
00:22:20,253 --> 00:22:22,767
Danny宝贝,干得漂亮
Danny boy,well done.

286
00:22:24,013 --> 00:22:25,526
让我们离开这儿
Let's get out of here.

287
00:22:27,893 --> 00:22:29,406
- 不好意思 - 什么事?
- Excuse me. - Yes?

288
00:22:29,493 --> 00:22:30,926
- 你是不是掉了狗? - 是的
- Have you lost a dog? - Yes.

289
00:22:31,013 --> 00:22:33,573
- 我想它可能在那家酒吧里 - 谢谢
- I think he might be in that pub. - Thank you.

290
00:22:37,973 --> 00:22:40,123
这是Vincent Cole
This is Vincent Cole.

291
00:22:40,373 --> 00:22:42,682
Vincent,这是Sam.Sam Richards
Vincent,this is Sam.Sam Richards.

292
00:22:43,413 --> 00:22:46,086
绅士们,我无意冒犯 但我有种强烈的感觉
No offence,gentlemen,but I get the distinct impression...

293
00:22:46,173 --> 00:22:48,084
我不会想听到接下来的对话
that I don't want to hear this conversation.

294
00:22:48,173 --> 00:22:50,926
- 谢谢,George - 我的荣幸
- Thank you,George. - My very great pleasure.

295
00:22:55,053 --> 00:22:58,443
George告诉我,你认得些人能帮我的忙
George tells me you have contacts in a field that I need help with.

296
00:22:58,533 --> 00:23:01,411
- 那方面的? - 警报系统
- Which is? - Alarm systems.

297
00:23:02,453 --> 00:23:04,921
你要的帮助是什么?
And what kind of help are you looking for?

298
00:23:05,293 --> 00:23:07,329
- 这个重要吗? - 如果你直说了,这个就不重要
- Does it matter? - Lf you're straight up,no.

299
00:23:07,413 --> 00:23:09,881
如果你是条子,我就需要听听你的解释
But if you're a cop,I need to hear you say the words...

300
00:23:09,973 --> 00:23:12,726
这样,我被捕的时候 能为这个诱捕辩护
so I can plead entrapment when I'm arrested.

301
00:23:15,093 --> 00:23:16,924
好了,我还有其他活儿要干
Okay,I have other things to do.

302
00:23:17,013 --> 00:23:18,332
对不起
Sorry.

303
00:23:22,293 --> 00:23:23,885
咖啡,谢谢
Coffee,thanks.

304
00:23:26,173 --> 00:23:27,811
我正计划抢个银行
I'm planning to rob a bank.

305
00:23:27,893 --> 00:23:29,645
都计划好了才想起要个搞定警报的?
And a bell man is an afterthought?

306
00:23:29,733 --> 00:23:31,132
我被放鸽子了
I've been let down.

307
00:23:32,293 --> 00:23:33,931
我自己可以进入银行
I can get into the bank.

308
00:23:34,653 --> 00:23:37,531
我可以解决外面的保安系统,一路到保险箱
I can deal with the outer security until I get to the vault.

309
00:23:37,613 --> 00:23:39,285
然后,我就需要帮助
That's where I need help.

310
00:23:40,013 --> 00:23:42,607
这是带有视网膜扫描的Locheim系统
It's a Locheim system with retinal scan.

311
00:23:42,693 --> 00:23:44,285
这需要一个专业人员
That needs a specialist.

312
00:23:44,373 --> 00:23:47,922
本来我有人可以搞定这个,但他昨晚被捕了
I had a guy lined up,but he was arrested last night.

313
00:23:48,253 --> 00:23:50,483
- 你能不能绕过这个? - 不行
- Can you bypass it? - No.

314
00:23:50,813 --> 00:23:54,123
唯一能够绕过这个安全系统的只有Victor Maher
The only one with the security override is Victor Maher.

315
00:23:54,373 --> 00:23:56,091
他是安全部门的头儿
The Head of Security.

316
00:23:57,093 --> 00:23:59,323
好吧,那你打算什么时候干?
Okay,so when are you going in?

317
00:23:59,653 --> 00:24:01,689
- 明晚 - 你的
- Tomorrow night. - Here you go,pal.

318
00:24:01,893 --> 00:24:03,246
谢谢
Thanks.

319
00:24:04,933 --> 00:24:07,686
那么?你能助我一臂之力吗?
So?Can you help?

320
00:24:08,453 --> 00:24:09,488
不能
No.

321
00:24:10,613 --> 00:24:12,649
但我认识一个人可以
But I know a man who can.

322
00:24:16,373 --> 00:24:17,601
这个小菜一碟
It's a piece of cake.

323
00:24:17,693 --> 00:24:21,003
你黑进它的视网膜扫描系统,然后改变它的设置
You hack into the retina scans and reprogram new settings.

324
00:24:21,333 --> 00:24:23,164
新设置是什么?
What are these new settings?

325
00:24:23,653 --> 00:24:26,884
你用自己的视网膜扫描,取代他们的
You take your own scanner,replace their retinal scans with your own.

326
00:24:26,973 --> 00:24:29,771
我可以给你这个软件,并在过程中知道你
I can give you the software and talk you through the process.

327
00:24:29,853 --> 00:24:32,128
不管怎样,记得两边的扫描
Whatever you do,remember to wipe both scans...

328
00:24:32,213 --> 00:24:34,044
都要在你离开前抹掉
on the computer memory before you leave...

329
00:24:34,133 --> 00:24:36,601
否则,就好像你把自己的指纹留在那
otherwise it's like leaving your fingerprints behind.

330
00:24:36,693 --> 00:24:39,127
等等.两边的扫描?
Hang on.Both scans?

331
00:24:40,333 --> 00:24:42,289
