00:35:36,053 --> 00:35:38,123
你俩怎么不说话了?
You two not talking,then?

502
00:35:39,493 --> 00:35:41,051
他不可理喻
He's impossible.

503
00:35:41,653 --> 00:35:44,929
所以你是因为他是Danny而生他的气?
So you're angry with Danny for being Danny?

504
00:36:02,373 --> 00:36:03,522
对不起
I'm sorry.

505
00:36:04,573 --> 00:36:06,211
没什么的
Don't worry about it.

506
00:36:14,133 --> 00:36:15,248
说真的
I mean it.

507
00:36:17,013 --> 00:36:19,049
我今天真的很开心
And I really did enjoy today.

508
00:36:24,853 --> 00:36:27,003
Stacie,Mickey找你
Stacie,Mickey wants you.

509
00:36:32,573 --> 00:36:35,406
所以你全知道,而把我蒙在鼓里?
So you knew all this and never said a word to me?

510
00:36:35,493 --> 00:36:38,053
是我不对Danny.对不起
That was wrong,Danny.I'm sorry.

511
00:36:38,133 --> 00:36:41,364
现在你们都知道了 我们是最强的团队
And that goes for all of you.We're strongest as a team.

512
00:36:42,253 --> 00:36:43,572
而我却忘记了
I tend to forget that.

513
00:36:43,653 --> 00:36:46,087
所以,如果你不搞定这个人 Danny就要进监狱
So if you don't set this guy up,Danny goes to prison.

514
00:36:46,173 --> 00:36:47,686
而如果你做了,你就要进监狱?
And if you do,you go instead?

515
00:36:47,773 --> 00:36:48,842
就是这样
That's about it.

516
00:36:48,933 --> 00:36:50,161
这真是笔好买卖
That's a good deal.

517
00:36:50,253 --> 00:36:52,005
我们现在是不是都漏了重点?
Aren't we all missing the point now?

518
00:36:52,093 --> 00:36:55,642
- 什么? - 我走,问题就解决了
- Which is? - Lf I go away,so does the problem.

519
00:36:55,733 --> 00:36:57,007
这不是选择
That's not an option.

520
00:36:57,093 --> 00:36:59,402
出于整个家族 三个火枪手的故事
Because of the whole family,musketeer thing.

521
00:36:59,493 --> 00:37:01,723
听着,我是新人,我会让你摆脱这个
Listen,I'm the new kid.I'll let you off that.

522
00:37:01,813 --> 00:37:03,929
不,因为那意味着他击败了我们
No,because it means he'll have beaten us.

523
00:37:04,013 --> 00:37:06,527
一直到那家伙打开保险箱,你才能拿到带子?
You don't get the tape till this guy's opened the vault?

524
00:37:06,613 --> 00:37:07,602
是的
Right.

525
00:37:07,693 --> 00:37:09,763
而少任何一个,保险箱都打不开
And he can't open the vault without one of us.

526
00:37:09,853 --> 00:37:10,968
没错
Right,too.

527
00:37:11,053 --> 00:37:13,203
一定程度上,你俩拴在一个绳子上
At which point you both get a tug.

528
00:37:13,293 --> 00:37:14,692
我不觉得我们有胜算
I don't see how we can win.

529
00:37:14,773 --> 00:37:17,333
如果我们进去了 你能不能从别的路走?
If we get you inside,can we get you out another way?

530
00:37:17,413 --> 00:37:19,165
不行,原路进去,原路返回
No,there's one way in,one way out.

531
00:37:19,253 --> 00:37:20,766
就像那个
It's like one of them things.

532
00:37:20,853 --> 00:37:23,208
三个笨蛋花4个小时挖一个洞
It takes three blokes four hours to dig a hole.

533
00:37:23,293 --> 00:37:27,047
如果6个人挖一个小点的洞要多久?
How long does it take six men to dig a smaller hole?

534
00:37:27,533 --> 00:37:29,012
算了吧Danny
Shut up,Danny.

535
00:37:29,093 --> 00:37:32,369
问题是,我们有没有其他主意?
The question is,do we have any ideas?

536
00:37:40,733 --> 00:37:42,849
我从来没这么高兴过
I don't think I've ever had so much fun.

537
00:37:42,933 --> 00:37:45,367
我很高兴我能帮上忙
I'm glad to have been of service.

538
00:37:45,533 --> 00:37:48,286
一直到胖女人唱歌,才会结束
It ain't all over till the fat lady sings.

539
00:37:49,333 --> 00:37:51,563
你打击我要我放弃吗
Don't you disappoint me by giving up.

540
00:37:52,093 --> 00:37:54,687
你给我的选择太苛刻
The options you've left me are rather limited.

541
00:37:55,453 --> 00:37:57,683
我没有给你任何选择
I haven't left you any options.

542
00:37:57,973 --> 00:37:59,770
就这么回事
That's how this thing works.

543
00:38:03,173 --> 00:38:05,050
那么,什么时候?
So,when?

544
00:38:05,853 --> 00:38:07,445
- 今晚 - 怎么做?
- Tonight. - How?

545
00:38:07,773 --> 00:38:10,890
他会黑入主机 然后改变视网膜扫描
He's hacking into the mainframe and resetting the retina scans.

546
00:38:10,973 --> 00:38:12,167
很聪明
Clever.

547
00:38:12,253 --> 00:38:13,845
但有个问题
But there's a problem.

548
00:38:14,213 --> 00:38:16,283
- 这要两个人 - 不
- It takes two people. - No.

549
00:38:17,213 --> 00:38:18,885
你做什么?
What are you going to do?

550
00:38:19,533 --> 00:38:21,251
我和他一起进去
I'm going in with him.

551
00:38:21,893 --> 00:38:24,282
但你早就知道了,是不是?
But you already knew that,didn't you?

552
00:38:24,453 --> 00:38:26,523
这好像是逻辑问题
Seemed like the logical thing.

553
00:38:30,133 --> 00:38:32,772
Albert会在场,把带子交给他
Albert will be there.Give him the tape.

554
00:38:32,853 --> 00:38:36,812
当我看到你的脸出现在sam边上 而且保险箱打开的时候
When I see your face next to Sam's,and the vault door open.

555
00:38:40,813 --> 00:38:43,327
看着警报在你们周围响一定很有意思
It's been a pleasure running rings round you.

556
00:39:12,213 --> 00:39:13,407
银行
The bank.

557
00:39:14,053 --> 00:39:16,567
Stacie,你和Danny 进行第一阶段
Stacie,you and Danny go and set up the first phase.

558
00:39:21,853 --> 00:39:23,525
我们需要见这里的老板
We'd like to see the manager,please.

559
00:39:23,613 --> 00:39:25,649
我能问问这个连接什么的?
Can I ask what it's in connection with?

560
00:39:25,733 --> 00:39:26,882
警察
Police.

561
00:39:29,733 --> 00:39:30,848
接下来Albert
Albert next.

562
00:39:30,933 --> 00:39:32,969
他们知道他是谁 所以我们需要一个掩护
They know who he is,so we'll need a disguise.

563
00:39:33,053 --> 00:39:35,726
Peregrin B.Winterhill三世,我想
Peregrin B.Winterhill III,I think.

564
00:39:35,813 --> 00:39:36,962
很好
Perfect.

565
00:39:37,053 --> 00:39:40,170
这个提供机会让我和sam进去
That should provide enough of a diversion for me and Sam to get in.

566
00:39:40,253 --> 00:39:42,721
我去拿东西,到那儿碰头,Danny
I'll pick up the materials and meet you there,Danny.

567
00:39:42,813 --> 00:39:44,485
你能准备份礼物吗?
Can you sort out the present?

568
00:39:55,733 --> 00:39:57,724
好了,干吧
Okay,let's do it.

569
00:40:25,973 --> 00:40:28,806
哦,我的天哪 我太尴尬了,你知道
Oh,my God,I'm so embarrassed,you know.

570
00:40:28,893 --> 00:40:30,804
对不起,我弯不下来
I'm sorry,I can't bend over.

571
00:40:56,773 --> 00:40:58,445
好了,第二步
Right,phase two.

572
00:40:58,573 --> 00:41:01,246
有两个门 Mickey搞定锁
Two gates at the side.Mickey will take care of the locks.

573
00:41:01,333 --> 00:41:02,846
会把你引向这扇门
Which will bring you to this door.

574
00:41:02,933 --> 00:41:05,970
到那时,Albert会去见Maher
By that time,Albert will just be arriving to meet Maher.

575
00:41:06,053 --> 00:41:08,567
这时候,所有人都要就位
You guys should be in position by this time.

576
00:41:08,653 --> 00:41:12,805
如果Maher真的如Albert所说的那么聪明 他很快就会发现
If Maher's as smart as Albert says he is,it won't take him long to figure it out.

577
00:41:12,893 --> 00:41:14,531
这样一来,他就会行动
From this point,he'll be running.

578
00:41:14,613 --> 00:41:16,729
你有三分半钟
That will give you three and a half minutes.

579
00:41:16,813 --> 00:41:17,962
行不行?
All right?

580
00:41:22,573 --> 00:41:25,690
我们知道他们会进来 我们什么没有办法
We know they'll be coming in,nothing we can do about that.

581
00:41:25,773 --> 00:41:28,765
所以他们会从这个方向出去 你明白我的意思吗?
So they'll be using this direction to get out.You understand me?

582
00:41:28,853 --> 00:41:31,208
这个方向,所以你们给我看好
This direction,so you stay alert.

583
00:41:32,053 --> 00:41:33,691
我们要抢先一步
We'll be one step ahead.

584
00:41:56,693 --> 00:41:57,967
准备好了吗?
You ready?

585
00:42:41,373 --> 00:42:44,490
Albert来得正是时候
Albert,just in time for the show.

586
00:43:08,133 --> 00:43:10,522
他们进去了,切换到保险箱里的摄像头
They're in.Switch to the vault cameras.

587
00:43:14,333 --> 00:43:16,528
- 让你的人各就各位<i> - 是的,先生</i>
- Get your men in position.<i>- Yes,sir.</i>

588
00:43:18,133 --> 00:43:20,693
这肯定让你很难堪,Albert
This must be very galling for you,Albert...

589
00:43:21,253 --> 00:43:23,608
看着你的人倒霉?
watching the downfall of your protg?

590
00:43:25,333 --> 00:43:26,402
抓到了
Gotcha.

591
00:43:27,293 --> 00:43:29,090
就是这个,来吧
That's the one.Come on.

592
00:43:29,173 --> 00:43:32,643
他们在保险箱里 关上外面的门,我这就下来
They're in the vault.Seal the outer door.I'm coming down.

593
00:43:32,933 --> 00:43:34,412
要不要跟我一块,Albert?
Care to join me,Albert?

594
00:43:34,493 --> 00:43:36,324
见证我辉煌的时刻
Watch my moment of glory.

595
00:43:36,413 --> 00:43:38,051
把带子给我
Just give me the tape.

596
00:43:43,733 --> 00:43:45,132
说"请"
Say "please."

597
00:43:48,733 --> 00:43:50,052
请
Please.

598
00:43:57,493 --> 00:43:58,608
先生
Sir.

599
00:43:59,573 --> 00:44:02,690
有烟,重复,有烟 带上毒气面罩
Smoke.I repeat,smoke.Get the gas masks.

600
00:44:13,693 --> 00:44:14,887
打开它
Unlock it.

601
00:44:17,493 --> 00:44:19,085
他们不可能进去的,先生
They won't get through,sir.

602
00:44:19,173 --> 00:44:21,243
烟在哪里?我闻到烟味
Where's the smoke?I smell smoke.

603
00:44:22,933 --> 00:44:24,252
怎么回事?
What's going on?

604
00:44:25,453 --> 00:44:27,205
安全系统被绕过了
Security override.

605
00:44:48,653 --> 00:44:50,052
行动!
Move!

606
00:45:00,653 --> 00:45:02,291
让开!
Move out of the way!

607
00:45:15,133 --> 00:45:17,772
他们重新安装过电路了,该死.
They've rerouted it.Oh,shit.

608
00:45:21,053 --> 00:45:22,566
快点!
Come on,quickly!

609
00:45:22,653 --> 00:45:24,769
他们肯定把它改到隔壁的门去了
They must have routed it next door.

610
00:45:32,133 --> 00:45:33,327
怎么回事?
What's going on?

611
00:45:33,413 --> 00:45:34,528
那儿是什么?
What's in there?

612
00:45:34,613 --> 00:45:37,525
你不能进去 是警局的监视
You can't go in there.It's police surveillance.

613
00:46:05,693 --> 00:46:07,604
快,回到保险库
Quick,back to the vault.

614
00:46:12,213 --> 00:46:13,851
很奇怪能在这里见到你
Fancy meeting you here.

615
00:46:15,733 --> 00:46:17,132
2分钟
Two minutes.

616
00:46:35,453 --> 00:46:36,602
找到了
Got it.

617
00:46:40,613 --> 00:46:42,444
- 走吧 - 你开玩笑?
- Let's go. - You are joking?

618
00:46:42,533 --> 00:46:43,852
我们不是小偷,Danny
We're not thieves,Danny.

619
00:46:43,933 --> 00:46:46,493
听着,为你自己着想一下 我是全能
Listen,speak for yourself.I'm very versatile.

620
00:46:46,573 --> 00:46:48,768
Mickey说拿了钻石就走
Mickey said to take the diamond and go.

621
00:46:48,853 --> 00:46:50,684
- Mickey说 - Danny
- Mickey says... - Danny.

622
00:46:50,773 --> 00:46:52,286
走吧
Let's go.

623
00:47:10,693 --> 00:47:11,967
他怎么了?
What's up with him?

624
00:47:12,053 --> 00:47:14,089
他只是要碰到私人危机了
He's just having a personal crisis.

625
00:47:14,173 --> 00:47:16,289
那儿有上百万镑
It's got millions in there.

626
00:47:51,813 --> 00:47:53,929
Milk的火车半小时离开
Milk train leaves in half an hour.

627
00:47:55,133 --> 00:47:57,601
- 我不知道该怎么谢你 - 那就不用谢了
- I don't know how to thank you. - Then don't.

628
00:47:57,693 --> 00:47:59,524
你真的帮了我大忙
You actually did me a favor.

629
00:48:00,813 --> 00:48:03,964
- 真的? - 我了解了自己很多
- Really? - I learnt a lot about myself.

630
00:48:04,053 --> 00:48:05,202
什么是重要的
What's important.

631
00:48:05,293 --> 00:48:07,523
我父亲对我来说是很重要的
My dad was important to me.

632
00:48:07,613 --> 00:48:09,012
我也是
Mine,too.

633
00:48:10,533 --> 00:48:11,886
你保重
You take care.

634
00:48:21,133 --> 00:48:23,522
哦,干得非常漂亮,不是吗?
Well,that went rather well,right?

635
00:48:23,613 --> 00:48:25,205
就像有人说的
Like the man said:

636
00:48:25,413 --> 00:48:28,883
直到胖女人唱歌,它才停止
It ain't over till the fat lady sings.

637
00:48:29,333 --> 00:48:31,244
这提醒了我
Which reminds me.

638
00:48:42,613 --> 00:48:43,807
什么?
Yes?

639
00:48:43,893 --> 00:48:46,009
干得好,Victor,但是没有雪茄
Nice try,Victor,but no cigar.

640
00:48:46,133 --> 00:48:48,772
但既然我这么享受这个游戏
But as I enjoyed playing the game so much...

641
00:48:48,853 --> 00:48:50,684
我们准备了份小礼物给你
we've arranged a little present for you...

642
00:48:50,773 --> 00:48:52,923
<i>如果你往你办公室窗外看</i>
<i>if you'd like to look out of your office window...</i>

643
00:48:53,013 --> 00:48:55,607
<i>我们好朋友Albert Stroller的一点心意</i>
<i>courtesy of our friend,Mr.Albert Stroller.</i>

644
00:49:25,653 --> 00:49:28,565
- 我真想看看他现在的表情 - 我也是
- I'd love to have seen his face. - Me,too.

645
00:49:29,333 --> 00:49:32,052
是的,在办公室里
Right,in the office.

646
00:49:32,373 --> 00:49:34,887
我去睡觉了,累死了
I'll turn in.I'm absolutely knackered.

647
00:49:36,973 --> 00:49:38,008
什么?
What?

648
00:49:38,493 --> 00:49:41,929
- 他有没有一刻是单独待在保险库里的? - 等等
- Was he left alone in the vault at any time? - Now,wait a minute.

649
00:49:42,013 --> 00:49:44,891
他忘了拿象棋,不得不折回
He forgot to leave the chess piece,had to go back.

650
00:49:44,973 --> 00:49:47,168
- 我什么也没干 - 哦,亲爱的
- I didn't do anything. - Oh,dear.

651
00:49:47,253 --> 00:49:49,323
Danny,你有什么要告诉我们的吗?
Danny,is there anything you'd like to tell us?

652
00:49:49,413 --> 00:49:51,563
- 你说什么呢? - 要我来搜身吗?
- What're you talking about? - Want me to frisk him?

653
00:49:51,653 --> 00:49:53,052
我什么也没干
I haven't done anything.

654
00:49:53,133 --> 00:49:55,522
好,那你不介意解了你的夹克吧
Good,then you won't mind unbuttoning your jacket.

655
00:49:55,613 --> 00:49:57,683
- 你们不信我? - 解了它
- You don't trust me? - Unbutton.

656
00:49:58,813 --> 00:49:59,928
继续,给我们看看
Go on,show us.

657
00:50:00,013 --> 00:50:02,766
这简直难以置信,我有...
That is unbelievable.What have I ever got...

658
00:50:02,853 --> 00:50:04,571
- 转身 - 冷静点
- Turn around. - Go easy.

659
00:50:04,653 --> 00:50:07,531
好了,做你想做的
All right,do what you want.

660
00:50:07,773 --> 00:50:09,570
等等,你居然没拿钱?
Hold on,you didn't take any money?

661
00:50:09,653 --> 00:50:12,121
不,我没有,伙计.但你知道吗?
No,I didn't,mate.But you know what?

662
00:50:12,213 --> 00:50:15,649
你们这么想我感到很吃惊,也有点生气
I'm shocked and a little bit upset that you thought that I did.

663
00:50:15,733 --> 00:50:17,132
谢谢,伙计们
Thanks,guys.

664
00:50:17,773 --> 00:50:19,809
好吧,那就由我来吧
Well,just must have been me then.

665
00:50:23,693 --> 00:50:24,762
你?
You?

666
00:50:24,853 --> 00:50:27,003
- 酬劳 - 你是小偷
- Expenses. - You're the thief.

667
00:50:30,013 --> 00:50:31,128
一人一叠
One each.

668
00:50:33,893 --> 00:50:35,372
除了
Except...

669
00:50:39,893 --> 00:50:41,292
我有两叠
I've got two.

670
00:50:51,293 --> 00:50:52,362
小偷
Thief.

671
00:51:14,653 --> 00:51:16,086
- 50便士 - 给你
- 50 pence. - There you go.

672
00:51:19,573 --> 00:51:20,642
谢谢
Thanks.

673
00:51:20,733 --> 00:51:22,803
等等,这是你余下的找头
Hang on,the rest of your change.

674
00:51:23,013 --> 00:51:24,162
对不起
Sorry.

675
00:51:24,253 --> 00:51:26,448
4个五便士,还有五个10便士
Four makes five and five's 10.

676
00:51:26,893 --> 00:51:30,044
我有1个的硬币 我有零钱,你把刚刚那个还我,Eddie?
I've got a 1 coin.Give me my 10 back,will you,Eddie?

677
00:51:30,133 --> 00:51:31,930
我该给你5便士和5个硬币
I'll give you 5 and five 1.

678
00:51:32,013 --> 00:51:33,844
帮我兑了这个零钱
Help me lose this change.

679
00:51:33,933 --> 00:51:35,286
最好看看
Better check it.

680
00:51:35,373 --> 00:51:38,126
- 等等,这里只有9个 - 对不起
- Hang on,there's only 9 here. - Sorry.

681
